rows.label: qev041004_MSG0001
rows.name:
Easy there, girl. Eaaasy...
Heh. This big dumb lunk loves us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0002
rows.name:
I told you feeding it treats before making our move
would pay off![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0003
rows.name: Now, who's ready to unwrap the presents?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0004
rows.name:
Heh heh. Ol' Zazazan was reeeal protective of this
here shipment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0005
rows.name: If it pans out, we may not need to work for weeks![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0006
rows.name:
...Huh? Hey, you're that [ST:gender p1=guy p2=gal ]! Lemme guess,
Zazazan hired you to steal his stuff back, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0007
rows.name:
That guy's cheaper than Scrooge, so if he's willing to
spend that much on this shipment, it's gotta be...what?
Jewels? Rare weapons?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0008
rows.name:
Whatever it is, I can't wait. And we'll have all the time
in the world to check it out once we're done with you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0009
rows.name:
One last job, boys! Time to show this punk not to stick
[ST:gender p1=his p2=her ] nose in our business![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0011
rows.name:
What the...? He's got a LOCK on it?
Oh, for the love of...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041004_MSG0012
rows.name:
Look around, idiots! Somebody find a rock or
something we can use to smash it open![ST:wait ]
